@startuml
title Viaverse Message Send / Safety Check — Activity Diagram
start
:User sends message;
:Validate session and participant;
:Validate conversation\njob/order state;
:Rate limit\nspam/abuse guard;
:Classify content\ntext/media/ref;
if (Unsafe?) then (yes)
  :Warn/block/message hold;
  :Queue moderation if needed;
else (no)
endif
:Persist message\nCassandra + metadata;
:Create delivery receipts;
:Notify participants;
:Emit MessageSent;
:Update conversation list\nlast message preview;
stop

note bottom
Unsafe message may be blocked, warned, held for review,
or allowed with event/audit depending on policy severity.
Never silently drop without user-visible state.
end note
@enduml
